com.worksap.nlp.sudachi

インタフェース InputTextBuilder<E>


  • public interface InputTextBuilder<E>
    A mutable sequence of characters. This class is used in InputTextPlugin.rewrite(com.worksap.nlp.sudachi.InputTextBuilder<?>) to modify the input text.

    • メソッドのサマリー

    • メソッドの詳細

      • replace

        void replace(int begin,
             int end,
             java.lang.String str)
        Replaces the characters in a substring of this sequence with characters in the specified String. The substring begins at the specified begin and extends to the character at index end - 1 or to the end of sequence if no such character exists.
        パラメータ:
        begin - the beginning index
        end - the ending index
        str - the replacement string
        例外:
        java.lang.StringIndexOutOfBoundsException - if begin is negative, greater than the length of the sequence, or greater than end.

      • getOriginalText

        java.lang.String getOriginalText()
        Returns the sequence before all of the replacements.
        戻り値:
        the sequence before all of the replacements

      • getText

        java.lang.String getText()
        Returns the sequence as String.
        戻り値:
        the sequence as String

      • build

        InputText<E> build()

        the immutable sequence of characters
